statements.sql: select `roles`.*, `model_has_roles`.`model_id` as `pivot_model_id`, `model_has_roles`.`role_id` as `pivot_role_id`, `model_has_roles`.`model_type` as `pivot_model_type` from `roles` inner join `model_has_roles` on `roles`.`id` = `model_has_roles`.`role_id` where `model_has_roles`.`model_id` in (2) and `model_has_roles`.`model_type` = 'App\\Models\\User'

select `md_produk`.`id`, `md_produk`.`nama_produk`, `md_produk`.`sku`, SUM(tb_penjualan_item.qty) as total_qty, SUM(tb_penjualan_item.qty * tb_penjualan_item.harga_jual) as total_amount, MAX(tb_penjualan.tanggal_penjualan) as last_sold_at from `md_produk` inner join `tb_penjualan_item` on `tb_penjualan_item`.`id_produk` = `md_produk`.`id` inner join `tb_penjualan` on `tb_penjualan`.`id_penjualan` = `tb_penjualan_item`.`id_penjualan` where `tb_penjualan`.`tanggal_penjualan` between '2025-12-01 00:00:00' and '2025-12-31 23:59:59' group by `md_produk`.`id`, `md_produk`.`nama_produk`, `md_produk`.`sku` having `total_qty` > 0 order by `total_qty` desc, `total_qty` desc limit 5
